translations: n.[畜牧] 授精；播种；受胎

sentences.sentence: Researcher Stephanie Belloc of the Eylau Centre for Assisted Reproduction in Paris and colleagues analyzed the outcomes of more than 21,000 intrauterine inseminations (IUIs).
sentences.translation: 位于巴黎旨在辅助生殖的Eylau中心的研究者，及其同事分析了超过21000宫内人工受精（IUIs）的病例结果。
